title: Historic landmark in Arraial do Cabo
text:
(90393) 2015-10-18 23:21 
Hi Ricardo, Pleasant view with the sand, a good brightness for colors, well composed with wall on ech side and this cross as focal point of your view, tfs. (87908) 2015-10-18 23:59 
Ola Ricardo, nice presentation of the historic place. Beautiful entrance, nice sandy road leading to the fishermen's harbour. The cross like in Portugal, with the short upper part. Fine composition, nice colours. Warm regards Malgo (91351) 2015-10-19 0:04 
Ola Ricardo, nice the view of the sandy beach with the cross to be the eye catching of the image as the landmark of it.The two stone columns create a beautiful and unique frame in the photo. Regards,Danos cargus (9612) 2015-10-19 8:32 
A very nice place , especillay an excellent shot with a perfect composition, magnificent colors, clear and bright..well done.!! All the best,
